01:10:01.790 --> 01:10:04.090
&gt;&gt; Mary Jo Bang: Yes.

01:10:07.590 --> 01:10:11.560 position:56%
I just want to add, because, my fear
has always been that I didn't want

01:10:11.560 --> 01:10:15.310
to be reductive about
complicated things.

01:10:15.310 --> 01:10:20.290
So, I think I tried to
complicate the language in order

01:10:20.290 --> 01:10:24.240 position:56%
to communicate complicated thoughts.

01:10:24.240 --> 01:10:29.240
But, I think that there are other
ways or I think I've achieved ways

01:10:29.240 --> 01:10:32.600
