01:10:54.290 --> 01:10:56.500
The Role of the Elegy.

01:10:56.500 --> 01:11:00.330
The role of the elegy
is to put a death mask

01:11:00.330 --> 01:11:03.540
on tragedy, A drape on the mirror.

01:11:03.540 --> 01:11:08.730
To bow to the cultural Debate over
the anesthetization of sorrow,

01:11:08.730 --> 01:11:13.610
Of loss, of the unbearable
Afterimage of the once material.

01:11:13.610 --> 01:11:17.130
To look for an imagined
Consolidation of grief

01:11:17.130 --> 01:11:22.000
So we can all be finished Once
and for all and genuinely shut

01:11:22.000 --> 01:11:25.600
up The cabinet of genuine
particulars.

01:11:25.600 --> 01:11:30.280
Instead there's the endless refrain
One hears replayed repeatedly

01:11:30.280 --> 01:11:35.550
Through the just ajar door: Some
terrible mistake has been made.

01:11:35.550 --> 01:11:38.920
What is elegy but the
attempt to rebreathe life

01:11:38.920 --> 01:11:43.970
into what the gone one once
was Before he grew to enormity.

01:11:43.970 --> 01:11:47.300
Come on stage and be yourself,
the elegist says to the dead.

01:11:47.300 --> 01:11:52.010
Show them Now after the fact
What you were meant to be:

01:11:52.010 --> 01:11:54.310
The performer of a live song.

01:11:54.310 --> 01:11:56.540
A shoe. Now bow.

01:11:56.540 --> 01:12:00.400
What is left but this:
The compulsion to tell.

01:12:00.400 --> 01:12:04.560
The transient distraction
of ink on cloth One scrubbed

01:12:04.560 --> 01:12:07.540 position:56%
and scrubbed but couldn't make less.

01:12:07.540 --> 01:12:10.150
Not then, not soon.

01:12:10.150 --> 01:12:11.610
Each day, a new caption

01:12:11.610 --> 01:12:15.280
